CustomField.formula:
IF( OR(
Available_Time__c <
DATETIMEVALUE(DATE(YEAR(DATEVALUE(Available_Time__c)),3,14) -(WEEKDAY(DATE(YEAR(DATEVALUE(Available_Time__c)),3,14))-1))+10/24,
/*If the date-time is before the second Sunday in March (end of wintertime)*/
Available_Time__c >= DATETIMEVALUE(DATE(YEAR(DATEVALUE(Available_Time__c)),11,7)
-(WEEKDAY(DATE(YEAR(DATEVALUE(Available_Time__c)),11,7))-1))+10/24
/*Or the date-time is after the first Sunday in November (start of wintertime)*/
),
HOUR(TIMEVALUE(Available_Time__c)) - 8,
/* Return GMT offset by 8 hours (ST) */
HOUR(TIMEVALUE(Available_Time__c)) - 7
/* Otherwise, return GMT offset by 7 hours (DST) */
)
